<footer class="sacred-footer">
  <div class="container footer-content">
    <div class="disclaimer-section">
      <p class="disclaimer-text type-body-lg">
        Rangkuman Alkitab tidak menggantikan kewajiban membaca Alkitab. Rangkuman ini ditujukan sebagai bahan pendamping. Disarankan selalu merujuk ke sumber asli.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="divider"></div>
    <div class="credits-section">
      <p class="credits-text type-label-md">
        Dibuat dengan 🤍 <a href="https://instagram.com/krisdntro" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="instagram-link">krisdntro</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .sacred-footer {
    background-color: var(--surface-container-low);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--outline-variant);
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem 0;
    margin-top: auto;
    width: 100%;
    transition: background-color var(--duration-normal), border-color var(--duration-normal);
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .disclaimer-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .disclaimer-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 40px;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--color-secondary);
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .credits-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .credits-text {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .instagram-link {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    position: relative;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast);
  }

  .instagram-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  .instagram-link::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: currentColor;
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: right;
    transition: transform var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out-expo);
  }

  .instagram-link:hover::after {
    transform: scaleX(1);
    transform-origin: left;
  }
</style>
